Why the build still fails (from the last successful log)
- After the controller javax -> jakarta fix, the next compilation run produced many errors (67). Major categories:
  1. EntityService method return types vs processors expectations:
     - EntityService.getItems(...) returns CompletableFuture<ArrayNode> (in the interface).
     - Many processors (MatchingProcessor, PersistLaureateProcessor, etc.) expect CompletableFuture<java.util.ArrayList<JsonNode>> and assign fut.get() to ArrayList. That type mismatch caused many errors.
  2. Missing fields/method names:
     - Processors reference methods such as job.getTechnicalId(), job.getManual(), job.getMaxRetries(), Laureate.getProvenance()/setProvenance(), Subscriber.getTechnicalId(), setTechnicalId(), etc.
