  (Lombok will generate getManual()/setManual())
- Ensure maxRetries exists (you already added maxRetries), and processors reference getMaxRetries() (Lombok will generate it).

3) Align Laureate fields referenced by processors
- If processors call setRawFullName(...) or similar, either:
